<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4502158>
    dc:description "Figs. 6–8. Male Ngirhaphium sivasothii, new species (Semakau, Singapore): 6, Habitus; 7, Genital capsule removed; 8, Wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4502158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4502160>
    dc:description "Figs. 9–10. Ngirhaphium sivasothii, new species (Semakau, Singapore): 9, Lateral view of genital capsule with left ventral surstylus at the front; 10, Dorsal view of cerci." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4502160/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4502168>
    dc:description "Figs. 17–19. Ventral view of male genital capsule: 17, Ngirhaphium sivasothii, new species; 18, N. murphyi; 19, N. caeruleum, new species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4502168/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

